Properties.EnglishScriptText: [[A goblin named Lodgok.]] A friendly goblin. He wants no part in Ranrok's fight.
[[They asked me not to say anything.]] Someone who knows Ranrok personally. They asked me not to mention their name to anyone.
[[That was cruel.]] Perhaps your uncle was right about you. You don't know when to stop.
[[You're not thinking straight.]] You don't know what you're saying. Take a breath for a moment.
